SELECT AVG(monthly_opened) AS monthly_average_opened
FROM (
    SELECT strftime('%m', "OpenDate") AS month, COUNT(*) AS monthly_opened
    FROM schools
    WHERE "County" = 'Alameda' 
      AND "DOCType" = 'Elementary School District'
      AND strftime('%Y', "OpenDate") = '1980'
    GROUP BY month
) AS monthly_counts;	----- bird -----	california_schools
